OL,4,CCovid: MPs want care home visiting
OL,5,Crights put into law
OL,6, The rights of care home residents to
OL,7, have visits from loved ones must be
OL,8, "underpinned" by law, according to a
OL,9, new report by cross-party MPs.
OL,11,FThe Joint Committee on Human Rights
OL,12,Fsaid it was "unacceptable" that some
OL,13,Fcare home providers had argued it was
OL,14,Fnot safe to follow government guidance.
OL,16,FSince April, care home residents in
OL,17,FEngland have been allowed two regular
OL,18,Fvisitors indoors as lockdown has eased.
OL,20,FBut the report said providers have not
OL,21,Ffelt bound by the guidance.
